<A>__{an obese man enters, smoking a cigar:}
<C>__{fat man}
<D>__{buzz.}
<A>__{buzz has already thrown the doors shut and sent the elevator into its power rise. norville, bracing himself now, sinks only a little under the g force.}
<C>__{buzz}
<D>__{say, buddy! who's the most liquid businessman on the street?}
<C>__{norville}
<D>__{well, i }
<C>__{buzz}
<D>__{waring hudsucker! na ha ha ha ha! say, buddy! when is the sidewalk fully dressed? when it's 'wearing' hudsucker! na ha ha ha!}
<A>__{he turns to look at norville.}
<C>__{buzz}
<D>__{...ya get it, buddy, it's a pun, it's a knee slapper, it's a play on jesus, joseph and mary, is that a blue letter?!}
<A>__{all heads in the elevator turn, aghast, to look, and those near norville shrink away.}
